_examples.MICRODATA:
A ProductModel gives a datasheet or vendor specification of a
product (in the sense of a prototypical description).  Use this type
when you are describing a product datasheet rather than an actual
product, e.g. if you are the manufacturer of the product and want to
mark up your product specification pages. For example: The ACME
Colorvision 123 specifiation on the ACME Corp. site for that model.

 
 ACME Colorvision 123
 The ACME Colorvision 123 is
  the leading-edge color TV from our company.
 EAN/UPC: 1234567890123

Recommendation: Try to provide identifiers (gtin13, gtin14, gtin8, mpn
properties) and link to you as the manufacturer (manufacturer
property) so that search engines can use your data to enrich offers of
your products found elsewhere.
_examples.PRE-MARKUP:
ACME Colorvision 123. The ACME Colorvision 123 is the leading-edge color TV from
our company. EAN/UPC: 1234567890123.

_pRange.rdfs:comment: A pointer to a base product from which this product is a variant. It is safe to infer that the variant inherits all product features from the base model, unless defined locally. This is not transitive.
_pRange.rdfs:label: isVariantOf

_pRange.descriptionZh: 产品的型号。可以是ProductModel类型的URL或者是型号标识的文本表示。ProductModel类型实体的URL可以来自外部来源。建议通过属性gtin8/gtin13/gtin14和mpn额外提供强产品标识。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The model of the product. Use with the URL of a ProductModel or a textual representation of the model identifier. The URL of the ProductModel can be from an external source. It is recommended to additionally provide strong product identifiers via the gtin8/gtin13/gtin14 and mpn properties.
_pRange.rdfs:label: model

_pRange.rdfs:comment: A pointer from a previous, often discontinued variant of the product to its newer variant.
_pRange.rdfs:label: predecessorOf

_pRange.descriptionZh: 新一代的产品之前的产品，通常是已经停产的产品
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A pointer from a newer variant of a product  to its previous, often discontinued predecessor.
_pRange.rdfs:label: successorOf

_properties.descriptionZh: 表示实体附加特征的属性值对（例如cnschema.org中没有匹配属性的产品功能或其他特性）
_properties.rdfs:comment:
A property-value pair representing an additional characteristics of the entitity, e.g. a product feature or another characteristic for which there is no matching property in cnschema.org.

Note: Publishers should be aware that applications designed to use specific cnschema.org properties (e.g. http://cnschema.org/width, http://cnschema.org/color, http://cnschema.org/gtin13, ...) will typically expect such data to be provided using those properties, rather than using the generic property/value mechanism.
_properties.rdfs:label: additionalProperty

_properties.descriptionZh: 该作品所面向的观众，也就是该作品为哪些群体创作。
_properties.rdfs:comment: An intended audience, i.e. a group for whom something was created.
_properties.rdfs:label: audience

_properties.descriptionZh: 此人或该创作性作品获得的奖金(奖项)。
_properties.rdfs:comment: An award won by or for this item.
_properties.rdfs:label: award

_properties.descriptionZh: 与该产品或服务相关的品牌，或者是由该组织或个人维护的品牌。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The brand(s) associated with a product or service, or the brand(s) maintained by an organization or business person.
_properties.rdfs:label: brand

_properties.rdfs:comment: A category for the item. Greater signs or slashes can be used to informally indicate a category hierarchy.
_properties.rdfs:label: category

_properties.rdfs:comment: The color of the product.
_properties.rdfs:label: color

_properties.rdfs:comment: The depth of the item.
_properties.rdfs:label: depth

_properties.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-12 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. The GTIN-12 is the 12-digit GS1 Identification Key composed of a U.P.C. Company Prefix, Item Reference, and Check Digit used to identify trade items. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
_properties.rdfs:label: gtin12

_properties.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-13 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. This is equivalent to 13-digit ISBN codes and EAN UCC-13. Former 12-digit UPC codes can be converted into a GTIN-13 code by simply adding a preceeding zero. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
_properties.rdfs:label: gtin13

_properties.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-14 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
_properties.rdfs:label: gtin14

_properties.rdfs:comment: The GTIN-8 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. This code is also known as EAN/UCC-8 or 8-digit EAN. See GS1 GTIN Summary for more details.
_properties.rdfs:label: gtin8

_properties.rdfs:comment: The height of the item.
_properties.rdfs:label: height

_properties.descriptionZh: 指明本产品是其他产品的附件或备件的指针。
_properties.nameZh: 是另一产品的附件或备件
_properties.rdfs:comment: A pointer to another product (or multiple products) for which this product is an accessory or spare part.
_properties.rdfs:label: isAccessoryOrSparePartFor

_properties.descriptionZh: 指明此产品是消耗品的另一产品（或多个产品）的指针。
_properties.rdfs:comment: A pointer to another product (or multiple products) for which this product is a consumable.
_properties.rdfs:label: isConsumableFor

_properties.rdfs:comment: A pointer to another, somehow related product (or multiple products).
_properties.rdfs:label: isRelatedTo

_properties.rdfs:comment: A pointer to another, functionally similar product (or multiple products).
_properties.rdfs:label: isSimilarTo

_properties.rdfs:comment: A predefined value from OfferItemCondition or a textual description of the condition of the product or service, or the products or services included in the offer.
_properties.rdfs:label: itemCondition

_properties.descriptionZh: 最小库存单元是指包含特定的自然属性与社会属性的商品种类，在零售连锁门店管理中通常称为“单品”。当一种商品而言，当他的品牌、型号、配置、花色、容量、生产日期、保质期、用途、价格、产地等属性与其他商品存在不同时，就是一个不同的最小存货单元。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The Stock Keeping Unit (SKU), i.e. a merchant-specific identifier for a product or service, or the product to which the offer refers.
_properties.rdfs:label: sku

_properties.rdfs:comment: The weight of the product or person.
_properties.rdfs:label: weight

_properties.rdfs:comment: The width of the item.
_properties.rdfs:label: width

_pTree.descriptionZh: 用来满足人们需求和欲望的物体或无形的载体。
_pTree.rdfs:comment: Any offered product or service. For example: a pair of shoes; a concert ticket; the rental of a car; a haircut; or an episode of a TV show streamed online.
_pTree.rdfs:label: Product

_properties.descriptionZh: 该项的一个附加类型， 通常用于从外部词典中向微数据语法添加更加具体的类型。它表示事物和事物本身所属的类之间的关系。在RDFa语法中, 对多类型最好使用‘typeof’属性这样的本地RDFa语法. Schema.org 工具对额外类型的理解较弱，特别是外部定义的额外类型。
_properties.rdfs:comment: An additional type for the item, typically used for adding more specific types from external vocabularies in microdata syntax. This is a relationship between something and a class that the thing is in. In RDFa syntax, it is better to use the native RDFa syntax - the 'typeof' attribute - for multiple types. Schema.org tools may have only weaker understanding of extra types, in particular those defined externally.
_properties.rdfs:label: additionalType

_properties.rdfs:comment: An alias for the item.

descriptionZh: 制造厂商用来提供每一个特殊类别产品的标识。

isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: A pointer to a base product from which this product is a variant. It is safe to infer that the variant inherits all product features from the base model, unless defined locally. This is not transitive.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: isVariantOf

isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: A pointer from a previous, often discontinued variant of the product to its newer variant.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: predecessorOf

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 新一代的产品之前的产品，通常是已经停产的产品
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: A pointer from a newer variant of a product  to its previous, often discontinued predecessor.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: successorOf

isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: A pointer to a base product from which this product is a variant. It is safe to infer that the variant inherits all product features from the base model, unless defined locally. This is not transitive.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: isVariantOf

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 产品的型号。可以是ProductModel类型的URL或者是型号标识的文本表示。ProductModel类型实体的URL可以来自外部来源。建议通过属性gtin8/gtin13/gtin14和mpn额外提供强产品标识。
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The model of the product. Use with the URL of a ProductModel or a textual representation of the model identifier. The URL of the ProductModel can be from an external source. It is recommended to additionally provide strong product identifiers via the gtin8/gtin13/gtin14 and mpn properties.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: model

isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: A pointer from a previous, often discontinued variant of the product to its newer variant.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: predecessorOf

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 新一代的产品之前的产品，通常是已经停产的产品
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: A pointer from a newer variant of a product  to its previous, often discontinued predecessor.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: successorOf

rdfs:comment: A datasheet or vendor specification of a product (in the sense of a prototypical description).
rdfs:label: ProductModel
